    autoslider: t_ae_pt_diff_slide to dataframe

    t_ae_pt_diff_slide_to_df.Rd

    autoslider: t_ae_pt_diff_slide to dataframe

    t_ae_pt_diff_slide_to_df(t_ae_pt_diff_slide)

    Arguments

    t_ae_pt_diff_slide

    an output from the autoslider function `t_ae_pt_diff_slide` See t_ae_pt_diff_slide

    Value

    dataframe object

    Examples

    library(dplyr)
adsl <- eg_adsl %>%
  mutate(TRT01A = factor(TRT01A, levels = c("A: Drug X", "B: Placebo")))
adae <- eg_adae %>%
  mutate(TRT01A = factor(TRT01A, levels = c("A: Drug X", "B: Placebo")))
adae$ATOXGR <- adae$AETOXGR
my_tbl <- t_ae_pt_diff_slide(adsl, adae, "TRT01A", 2)

t_ae_pt_diff_slide_to_df(my_tbl)
